review_title: Do not buy this camera. Save yourself time and spend an extra 20 bucks for a way better camera!
reviews: I had rated this 4 stars but I am changing my review after trying to use this camera for a class session. I used it to fb video chat and it worked ok. But in the class meet the video was so bad you could barely make out anything on our screen, and the sound would not work even tho it was set up correctly. It worked fine on fb but in the class meet it was not acceptable. I would not recommend this camera. It was an absolute waste of money.
